    "However, we have removed the final convolutional layer from the RRDB architecture as we aim not to obtain SR outcomes but rather to concentrate on the concealed LR image particulars.",
    "Additionally, we have removed the BN layers due to findings in pertinent literature 1, 25, 38 indicating their potential to introduce unwanted artifacts and constrain the model's capacity for generalization.",
